{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n163\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 1\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 81 + 54 + 3 = 138\u2081\u2080\n\n545\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 405 + 36 + 5 = 446\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n138 \u00d7 446 = 138 \u00d7 (400 + 46) = 55,200 + 6,348 = 61,548\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n61548 \u00f7 9 = 6838 r 6\n6838 \u00f7 9 = 759 r 7\n759 \u00f7 9 = 84 r 3\n84 \u00f7 9 = 9 r 3\n9 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 0\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: 103376\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n103376\u2089 = 1\u00d759049 + 0\u00d76561 + 3\u00d7729 + 3\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 6\u00d71\n= 59049 + 0 + 2187 + 243 + 63 + 6 = 61,548\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n103376", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 450}